Oak Crest Mobile Park
An All Ages/Family Community
Located in West Orange County,  developed in 1969 by Robert N. Jernigan and has remained family owned and operated.
Surrounded by lakes and secluded from the busy streets of Orlando.  We are proud to be considered "Affordable Living"
Amenities
Club House
Laundry
Lake View Picnic Area
Basketball Court and Playground
Storage Lot
Municipal Water and Sewer System
Monthly Site Rent Includes:
Water
Sewer
Garbage, yard and recycling pick up
Large area mowing
(Call for site rates)
Home sites are leased on a yearly basis; by application approval. Which includes credit and criminal background check
Minutes away from: Shopping, Businesses, Medical Facilities, Churches, Orlo Vista Elementary School,
Fire Station #30, Valencia College, Universal Studios, The Mall at Millenia, and the EW408, Colonial Dr/Hwy 50
